# SOCIALCLUB::SC_HAS_NEW_ROCKSTAR_MSG

## Summary
Returns whether there is a new Rockstar Message.  If this returns TRUE, script can safely collect the new message via SC_HAS_NEW_ROCKSTAR_MSG

## Returns
* **BOOL**
